<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,312,1911,1936]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">
<typeStatus box="[151,210,1911,1936]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">Type</typeStatus>
species:
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius, 1794" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[322,704,1911,1936]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="florea">
<emphasis box="[322,516,1911,1936]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">Voluccella florea</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[526,704,1911,1936]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius, 1794</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(the 1st of three originally included species), automatic as the result of 
<bibRefCitation author="Latreille, P. A." box="[254,451,1948,1973]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" refId="ref5237" refString="Latreille, P. A. (1810) Considerations generales sur l'ordre naturel des animaux composant les classes des crustaces, des arachnides, et des insectes; avec un tableau methodique de leurs genres, disposes en familles. F. Schoell, Paris, 444 pp." type="book" year="1810">Latreille’s (1810)</bibRefCitation>
designation of 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[630,935,1948,1973]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="florea">
<emphasis box="[630,822,1948,1973]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">Voluccella florea</emphasis>
Fabricius
</taxonomicName>
as 
<typeStatus box="[976,1024,1948,1972]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">type</typeStatus>
species for 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille, 1802" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[1165,1396,1948,1973]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Usia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1165,1218,1949,1972]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">Usia</emphasis>
Latreille, 1802
</taxonomicName>
, an unnecessary new replacement name for 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius, 1794" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[606,910,1984,2009]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[606,723,1984,2009]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">Voluccella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[732,910,1984,2009]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius, 1794</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius, 1794" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[923,1223,1984,2009]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[923,1040,1984,2009]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="76">Voluccella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[1048,1223,1984,2009]" pageId="3" pageNumber="76" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius, 1794</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was placed on the 
<emphasis box="[151,876,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Official Index of Rejected and Invalid Generic Names in Zoology</emphasis>
(Name No. 844) by the 
<bibRefCitation author="International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="83 - 120" refId="ref4947" refString="International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature (1957) Opinion 441. Validation under the Plenary Powers of the names for five genera in the Order Diptera (Class Insecta) published in 1762 by Geoffroy (E. L.) in the work entitled &quot; Histoire abregee des insectes qui se trouvent aux environs de Paris. &quot; (Opinion supplementary to Opinion 228.) Opinions and Declarations Rendered by the International Commission of Zoological Nomenclature, 15, 83 - 120." type="journal article" year="1957">International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature (1957: 88)</bibRefCitation>
and is therefore a senior but invalid synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille" authorityName="Latreille" box="[1272,1436,188,213]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Usia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1272,1325,189,212]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Usia</emphasis>
Latreille
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[158,310,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Bombyliidae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="77" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,968]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,260,285]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
The name 
<taxonomicName authority="Geoffroy, 1762" authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1762" box="[452,743,260,285]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Volucella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[452,556,260,285]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Volucella</emphasis>
Geoffroy, 1762
</taxonomicName>
, as originally proposed for species of 
<taxonomicName box="[1195,1312,260,285]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Syrphidae</taxonomicName>
, was cited under 
<taxonomicName authority="Linnaeus, 1758" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" box="[230,623,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Anthomyiidae" genus="Musca" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pellucens">
<emphasis box="[230,426,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Musca pellucens</emphasis>
Linnaeus, 1758
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[682,935,295,320]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" refId="ref4560" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1775) Systema entomologiae, sistens insectorum classes, ordines, genera, species, adiectis synonymis, locis, descriptionibus, observationibus. Kortii, Flensbvrgi et Lipsiae [= Flensburg and Leipzig], [30] + 832 pp. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 36510" type="book" year="1775">Fabricius (1775: 773</bibRefCitation>
, misspelled as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[1129,1246,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1129,1246,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 1781: 435, as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[151,268,332,357]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,268,332,357]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), and under 
<taxonomicName authority="(Linnaeus, 1758)" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" box="[416,825,332,357]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Syrphus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pellucens">
<emphasis box="[416,622,332,357]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Syrphus pellucens</emphasis>
(Linnaeus, 1758)
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[872,1113,332,357]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius (1794: 279</bibRefCitation>
, as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1762" box="[1159,1263,332,357]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Volucella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1159,1263,332,357]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Volucella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 1805: 224, as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[151,268,367,392]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,268,367,392]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,968]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[199,445,404,429]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius (1794: 412)</bibRefCitation>
deliberately proposed a different usage of the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[1049,1166,404,429]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1049,1166,404,429]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for three species of the family 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[233,381,439,464]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Bombyliidae</taxonomicName>
, and this usage qualifies as a new available name. Two original spellings of the name were given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[255,449,476,501]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius (1794)</bibRefCitation>
: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[463,580,476,501]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[463,580,476,501]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(p. 412) and 
<emphasis box="[743,853,476,501]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Volvicella</emphasis>
(p. [5] of the unnumbered index). Acting as First Reviser, 
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[254,446,511,536]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" refId="ref4772" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1805) Systema antliatorum secundum ordines, genera, species adiectis synonymis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. C. Reichard, Brunsvigae [= Brunswick], xiv + 15 - 372 + [1 (errata)] + 30 pp." type="book" year="1805">Fabricius (1805)</bibRefCitation>
selected 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[561,678,511,536]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[561,678,511,536]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the correct original spelling (
<emphasis box="[1071,1130,511,536]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Code</emphasis>
Article 24.2.4). 
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." pageId="4" pageNumber="77" refId="ref4772" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1805) Systema antliatorum secundum ordines, genera, species adiectis synonymis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. C. Reichard, Brunsvigae [= Brunswick], xiv + 15 - 372 + [1 (errata)] + 30 pp." type="book" year="1805">Fabricius (1805: 114–116)</bibRefCitation>
included six species of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[665,810,548,573]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Bombyliidae</taxonomicName>
in his 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[893,1010,548,573]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[893,1010,548,573]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Meigen, J. W." box="[1027,1196,548,573]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="153 - 314" refId="ref5315" refString="Meigen, J. W. (1804) Klassifikazion und Beschreibung der europaischen zweiflugeligen Insekten. (Diptera Linn.). Erster Band. K. Reichard, Braunschweig [= Brunswick]. Abt. 1, xxviii + 1 - 152, pls. 1 - 8; Abt. 2, vi + 153 - 314, pls. 9 - 15." type="journal article" year="1804">Meigen (1804)</bibRefCitation>
initially adopted the usage of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[252,369,583,608]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[252,369,583,608]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
proposed by Fabricius, but the name was subsequently replaced by 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille." authorityName="Latreille." box="[1131,1293,583,608]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Usia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1131,1184,584,607]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Usia</emphasis>
Latreille.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,968]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">
<taxonomicName authority="Geoffroy" authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1762" box="[199,413,620,645]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Volucella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[199,303,620,645]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Volucella</emphasis>
Geoffroy
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[470,699,620,645]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[470,587,620,645]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
Fabricius
</taxonomicName>
are not homonyms because the names differ by one letter (
<emphasis box="[1377,1436,620,645]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Code</emphasis>
Article 56.2). 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J." box="[313,744,655,680]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="1 - 64" refId="ref4521" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J. (2003) World catalog of bee flies (Diptera: Bombyliidae): Corrigenda and addenda. Zootaxa, 300, 1 - 64." type="journal article" year="2003">Evenhuis &amp; Greathead (2003: 10–11)</bibRefCitation>
understood this and believed therefore that the widely used generic name 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille, 1802" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[317,551,692,717]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Usia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[317,370,693,716]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Usia</emphasis>
Latreille, 
<quantity box="[495,551,692,717]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.57708" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" unit="in" value="1802.0">1802</quantity>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[597,745,692,717]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Bombyliidae</taxonomicName>
, originally proposed as a replacement name for 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius, 1794" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1319,1436,692,717]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[151,332,727,752]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius, 1794</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, was threatened as a junior synonym. These authors were aware that 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[1150,1381,727,752]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1150,1267,727,752]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
Fabricius
</taxonomicName>
was invalid as the result of a ruling by the 
<bibRefCitation author="International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[612,1380,764,789]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="83 - 120" refId="ref4947" refString="International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature (1957) Opinion 441. Validation under the Plenary Powers of the names for five genera in the Order Diptera (Class Insecta) published in 1762 by Geoffroy (E. L.) in the work entitled &quot; Histoire abregee des insectes qui se trouvent aux environs de Paris. &quot; (Opinion supplementary to Opinion 228.) Opinions and Declarations Rendered by the International Commission of Zoological Nomenclature, 15, 83 - 120." type="journal article" year="1957">International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature (1957: 88)</bibRefCitation>
(see 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L." box="[151,362,799,824]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" refId="ref4485" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. (1991) World catalog of genus-group names of bee flies (Diptera: Bombyliidae). Bishop Museum Bulletins in Entomology, 5, vii + 105 pp." type="book" year="1991">Evenhuis 1991: 77</bibRefCitation>
) but were concerned that this ruling could be challenged and potentially overturned (as allowed under 
<emphasis box="[222,281,836,861]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Code</emphasis>
Article 80.4) because it was based on the misinterpretation of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" box="[989,1106,836,861]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[989,1106,836,861]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a misspelling of 
<taxonomicName authority="Geoffroy" authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1762" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Volucella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1332,1436,836,861]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Volucella</emphasis>
Geoffroy
</taxonomicName>
(N. Evenhuis, pers. comm.). To permanently fix the priority of 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille, 1802" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[1013,1247,871,896]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Usia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1013,1066,872,895]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Usia</emphasis>
Latreille, 1802
</taxonomicName>
over 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius, 1794" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1794" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Voluccella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1319,1436,871,896]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">Voluccella</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius, J. C." box="[151,328,908,933]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="5" refId="ref4677" refString="Fabricius, J. C. (1794) Entomologia systematica emendata et aucta. Secundum classes, ordines, genera, species adjectis synonimis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Tom. IV. C. G. Proft, Fil. et Soc., Hafniae [= Copenhagen], [6] + 472 + [5] pp." type="journal article" year="1794">Fabricius, 1794</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J." box="[339,675,908,933]" pageId="4" pageNumber="77" pagination="1 - 64" refId="ref4521" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J. (2003) World catalog of bee flies (Diptera: Bombyliidae): Corrigenda and addenda. Zootaxa, 300, 1 - 64." type="journal article" year="2003">Evenhuis &amp; Greathead (2003)</bibRefCitation>
declared the former as a 
<emphasis box="[958,1151,909,932]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">nomen protectum</emphasis>
and the latter as a 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="77">nomen oblitum</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
